# рҹ§  Driver Drowsiness Detection using Deep Learning

## рҹ“Ң Project Overview

Driver fatigue is one of the leading causes of road accidents. This project presents a **non-intrusive, vision-based Driver Drowsiness Detection System** that analyzes facial features such as **eye closure and yawning** using Deep Learning.

The system classifies driver states and tracks fatigue progression over time to enhance road safety and enable real-time alert systems.

---

## рҹҺҜ Objectives

* Detect **eye state** (Open / Closed)
* Detect **mouth state** (Yawn / No Yawn)
* Combine predictions to determine **fatigue level**
* Analyze **fatigue progression over time**

